snippet.title: Whatever happened to Slavia: my New game's Demo
snippet.description:
Return of the Hlev
Play the Myths are 100% True Demo here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3047510/Myths_are_100_True/

ClayGod: https://www.youtube.com/@ClayGod
Progress Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLR3vFUGjIviTJrIHY3gnZrOYucqzWqprl

mikelwave: https://www.youtube.com/@MGZone
Slavija: Bottle Edition: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y3VNhwyeUIE

Random GTA SA Myth video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?t=28&v=yK72HG6oOPs

mudeth's channel:
https://www.youtube.com/c/mudeth

the faint "why isn't this working" for that one joke near the end is Verigl from one of the cutscenes in Devil May Cry 3, i just felt weird not sourcing that.

I don't remember who coded the original slavia prototype, i'm sorry
